'''广藏市场'''（{{lang-ko|광장시장}}），旧称'''东大门市场'''，是[[韩国|韩国]][[首尔市|首尔市]][[钟路区|钟路区]]的一个传统[[市场|市场]]。该市场是韩国历史最悠久，规模最大的传统市场之一，占地4.2万平方米，拥有超过5000间商店和20000名员工。每天约有6.5万人逛这个市场。<ref>{{cite web|author1=Yun Suh-young|title=Gwangjang Market: Seoul's quirky foodie paradise|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/02/203_130483.html|website=The Korea Times|accessdate=2015-02-25|date=2013-02-14|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112041/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/02/203_130483.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Choi|first1=Won-hyeong|title=Taste of Humanism in the 107-Year-Old Memories of Gwangjang Market|url=http://www.koreafocus.or.kr/design3/BookReview/view.asp?volume_id=126&content_id=104201&category=I|website=Korea Focus|publisher=[[韩民族日报|韩民族日报]]|accessdate=2015-04-22|date=2012-07-21|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092807/http://www.koreafocus.or.kr/design3/BookReview/view.asp?volume_id=126&content_id=104201&category=I|archive-date=2015-05-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==位置==
市场在[[鐘路5街站|鐘路5街站]]和[[乙支路4街站|乙支路4街站]]附近。<ref>{{cite web|author1=Shim Hyun-chul|title=Gwangjang Market|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2007/06/153_5214.html|website=The Korea Times|accessdate=2015-02-25|date=2007-06-21|language=en|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225170346/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2007/06/153_5214.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

